Initial Setup

1. Install the bundler gem

sudo gem install bundler

2. Run gem bundle in the application root

gem bundle

3. Set up a database.yml

4. create/migrate your databases

5. Start up the app



Debian/Ubuntu Notes
====================

If you start up the server and get the following error:
  no such file to load -- net/https (RuntimeError)
Install the following package:
  sudo apt-get install libopenssl-ruby

